@startuml High-Level Flow Diagram

title High-Level Booking Flow

actor User
participant "Frontend (HTML/JS)" as Frontend
participant "TheatreController" as TheatreCtrl
participant "MovieController" as MovieCtrl
participant "BookingController" as BookingCtrl
participant "TheatreService" as TheatreSvc
participant "MovieService" as MovieSvc
participant "BookingService" as BookingSvc
participant "TheatreRepository" as TheatreRepo
participant "MovieRepository" as MovieRepo
participant "BookingRepository" as BookingRepo
database "MySQL DB" as DB

== User Selects City ==
User -> Frontend: Select city
Frontend -> TheatreCtrl: GET /api/theatres/cities
TheatreCtrl -> TheatreSvc: getCities()
TheatreSvc -> TheatreRepo: findDistinctLocations()
TheatreRepo -> DB: SELECT DISTINCT location FROM theatres
DB --> TheatreRepo: Cities list
TheatreRepo --> TheatreSvc: Cities
TheatreSvc --> TheatreCtrl: Cities
TheatreCtrl --> Frontend: Cities displayed

== User Selects Movie in City ==
User -> Frontend: Select movie in city
Frontend -> MovieCtrl: GET /api/movies/city/{city}
MovieCtrl -> MovieSvc: getMoviesByCity(city)
MovieSvc -> MovieRepo: findMoviesByCity(city)
MovieRepo -> DB: Query movies via shows/theatres
DB --> MovieRepo: Movies in city
MovieRepo --> MovieSvc: Movies
MovieSvc --> MovieCtrl: Movies
MovieCtrl --> Frontend: Movies displayed

== User Selects Theatre ==
User -> Frontend: Select theatre for movie in city
Frontend -> TheatreCtrl: GET /api/theatres/city/{city}/movie/{movieId}
TheatreCtrl -> TheatreSvc: getTheatresByCityAndMovie(city, movieId)
TheatreSvc -> TheatreRepo: findTheatresByCityAndMovie(city, movieId)
TheatreRepo -> DB: Query theatres via shows
DB --> TheatreRepo: Theatres
TheatreRepo --> TheatreSvc: Theatres
TheatreSvc --> TheatreCtrl: Theatres
TheatreCtrl --> Frontend: Theatres displayed

== User Selects Show and Seats ==
User -> Frontend: Select show and seats
Frontend -> Frontend: Prepare BookingRequestDTO

== API Call ==
Frontend -> BookingCtrl: POST /api/bookings/book (BookingRequestDTO)
BookingCtrl -> BookingSvc: bookSeats(BookingRequestDTO)

== Business Logic ==
BookingSvc -> BookingSvc: Create PENDING booking
BookingSvc -> BookingRepo: Validate show and seats
BookingRepo -> DB: Query show/seat data
DB --> BookingRepo: Return data
BookingRepo --> BookingSvc: Validation result

BookingSvc -> BookingSvc: Check if seats available
BookingSvc -> BookingSvc: Simulate payment processing

alt Payment Successful
    BookingSvc -> BookingRepo: Mark seats as booked
    BookingRepo -> DB: Update ShowSeats
    DB --> BookingRepo: Updated
    BookingRepo --> BookingSvc: Seats booked

    BookingSvc -> BookingRepo: Update booking to CONFIRMED
    BookingRepo -> DB: Update Booking
    DB --> BookingRepo: Updated
    BookingRepo --> BookingSvc: Booking confirmed

    BookingSvc --> BookingCtrl: BookingConfirmationDTO
    BookingCtrl --> Frontend: HTTP 201 (Confirmation)
    Frontend --> User: Show booking success
else Payment Failed
    BookingSvc -> BookingRepo: Update booking to FAILED
    BookingRepo -> DB: Update Booking
    DB --> BookingRepo: Updated
    BookingRepo --> BookingSvc: Booking failed

    BookingSvc --> BookingCtrl: Throw PaymentProcessingException
    BookingCtrl --> Frontend: HTTP 409 (Payment failed)
    Frontend --> User: Show error
end

== Locks Released ==
note right: Locks automatically released on transaction end

@enduml